an1.21:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign nginder ki-an moorditj, mokin wil-ye kaart. Ki-an moorditj kaart wil-ye kaart.
an1.22:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign nginder penign mogin ne, yakka kaart. Ghain kwabba kaart moorditj.
an1.23:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign nginder ki-an penign mokin ne, be mogin bulla wayarn
